Package edu.umw.cpsc.humantrafficking

Class Summary
HumanTrafficking A simulation of global human trafficking; specifically forced prostitution.
HumanTraffickingWithUI The class controlling MASON-oriented visual display for the simulation.
Location Locations represent places where human trafficking victims can be present.
Route A Route represents a known pathway of human trafficking victims exploited by a trafficking network.
StatsPrinter Utility class to periodically dump statistical output from simulation to flat files.
Victim A Victim represents a woman being abducted for sex trafficking.
